<h2 id="100">7. Automatically sending shipping confirmations</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up the following event procedures in order to inform Klarna UK when items are shipped, orders are cancelled and credit notes or refunds are paid. Set up an <a href="/en/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically send shipping confirmations to Klarna. Payment providers usually wait for the shipping confirmation from the merchant before they disburse and transfer the amount paid by the customer to the merchant’s account.</p>
